==Portuguese==

===Pronunciation===
*/aˈve(x)/

===Etymology===
Latin [[habere]].

===Verb===
'''haver'''
# ([[de#{{pt}}|de]] + ''infinitive'') [[should]];
#: "''Amanhã, '''hei''' de ver o filme.''" - Tomorrow, I should watch the movie.
# (past + ''regular participle'') [[had]];
#: "'''Eu já '''tinha''' entrado quando você chegou.'''" - I had already got in when you arrived.
# (present + ''regular participle'') [[have]] [[been]];
#: "''Eu '''tenho''' estudado muito, nos últimos dias.''" - I have been studying a lot, last days
# (''impersonal'') [[There is|there is]], [[there are]].
#: "'''''Há''' um banco aqui perto.''" - There is a bank nearby.

